{
  "stem": "14190.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So I did this.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I-- I came.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I woke her up and held the bread right next to her face.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And-- and when she saw the bread, she didn't-- she started trying to wake to eat.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And lo and behold, few seconds later, a bubble started to come out from her mouth, from her nose.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I thought, oh my gosh, I didn't know that that was soap that they were making, their own soap that looked like honey.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Oh my.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I thought that-- I thought that-- I wanted-- I tell her not-- I wanted to take away from her the bread and everything.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "She wouldn't let me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Then she started to make noises.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Soap and bubbles and everything she ate.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And then I was looking at her, thinking that any moment she's going to die, probably, you know, scared as I was.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "But still-- still I took her and dress her-- dress her.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "We were never undressed really, to sleep.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "We were-- most of the time, we slept in our clothes.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And just we had a little-- it's called in Russian, called [RUSSIAN] we put on.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "It's like a quilted little jacket.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "So I put this on her and-- and snuck out of-- of there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "The dog barked a few times, but he knew us by then.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we snuck out and went on a road.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't know where to go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had no idea.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't-- didn't know how far we are from Vilnius.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I didn't know where to go, just on the road.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And how far we went, also I cannot tell you exactly.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It seemed to me like forever, but by then we were very cold.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I noticed that on the road, they had like a place that they're making bricks.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
